headline: MarketAxess to Participate in the Raymond James 2025 Institutional Investors Conference
summary: NEW YORK, February 24, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced that Chris Concannon, Chief Executive Officer, will participate in the Raymond James 2025 Institutional Investors Conference on March 3, 2025.
